rows.label: qst200910_msg001
rows.name:
You're here to rescue
me? Oh, thank god.

rows.label: qst200910_msg002
rows.name:
It's not safe here. We
should head back to Saets
Lumber Co. immediately.

rows.label: qst200910_msg004
rows.name:
Don't worry, they didn't hurt
me. I can walk just fine.

rows.label: qst200910_msg005
rows.name:
I'm sure everyone'll be wondering
where I got to, eh? We should hurry
back and show them I'm safe.
